.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, singing, chess, skydiving
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, horror, scientific, superhero, time-travel
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, gospel, indie, pop, techno
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the fan of country is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of indie##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby          | chess        | card-games       | singing | drawing   | skydiving  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | horror | drama   | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | techno     | gospel | country | indie     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

