.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, april, june, september, august
There are 5 different nationalities: american, egyptian, german, nigerian, turkish
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish, hamster, snake
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, parkour, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the american##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 4. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the german is the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
| Birthday      | july        | september   | april  | june         | august |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | american   | turkish | nigerian      | german   |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish   | snake   | ferret        | hamster  |
| Sport         | baseball   | basketball | parkour | skateboarding | cricket  |

