.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-9::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, tea, water
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, gardening, magic-tricks, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, electronic, folk, r&b, soul
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar, vegafina, siglo, ritmeester
 1. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the montecristo-smoker is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person drinking water is the fan of electronic##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of folk##1
12. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |      4       |     5      |
| Beverage      | water       | iced-tea   | tea        | 7up          | juice      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | filmmaking | gardening  | magic-tricks | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | country    | soul       | folk         | r&b        |
| Cigar     | montecristo    | siglo    | ritmeester | bolivar         | vegafina  |

