 5. the person who likes amber is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
12. the person who likes blue is the fan of house##1
13. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Color   | blue  | brown | ebony | amber  | emerald  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | country    | blues        | reggae | folk     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

