5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, havana, blend, tiparillo, dunhill
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, british, italian, polish, thai
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is the thai##1
